                        <interp inst="t18470405-name-548" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH HOOLEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 42.) I received the prisoner into cus<lb></lb>tody, and five cheroots from his master—another cheroot was produced at the station—he said he was very sorry for what he had done, he hoped Mr. Benjamin would forgive him, and he would not do so any more.</p>
